对于每种代谢物 79611 : 171，挑选出至少在80%样本中出现的代谢物 对于每种mOTU 300 : 171，挑选出至少在5%样本中出现的mOTU

setwd("C:/Users/zoumanli/Desktop")
data1 <- read.table("motu.txt", header = T, fileEncoding = "utf-8")
data2 <- read.table("metabolism.txt", header = T, fileEncoding = "utf-8")
data1[is.na(data1)] = 0
data2[is.na(data2)] = 0
for (i in 1:length(data2)) {
    if (sum(data2[i, ] == 0) > 34.1) {
        data2 <- data2[-i, ]
    }
}
dim(data2)
## [1] 7509  171
center <- sweep(data2, 1, apply(data2, 1, min), "-")
R <- apply(data2, 1, max) - apply(data2, 1, min)
data2_new <- sweep(center, 1, R, "/")
data21 <- data2_new[1:5000, ]
mylist <- list(data1, data21)
result <- jive(mylist)
## Estimating  joint and individual ranks via permutation...

## JIVE algorithm converged after  3  iterations.
## Re-estimating  joint and individual ranks via permutation...
